name: Street Credit
short_description: Street Credit (CRED) is the Exchange Token for the leading BSC AMM & Most Gangster Exchange Ever Created StreetSwap.vip.
description: Street Credit (CRED) is the Exchange Token for the leading BSC AMM & Most Gangster Exchange Ever Created StreetSwap.vip. CRED is created by staking THUGS. The THUGS value per CRED continues to grow as Exchange Fees are used to buy-back THUGS and fund the CRED contract autonomously.
